{"tid":413144,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"6060國暗升12.2% 報67蚊","createTime":"2017-09-25T09:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T00:05:07.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca3244c772a0bf524114050351eb4ff03e8494fe","tid":413144,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"《新股情報》眾安(06060)暗盤價於67元錄得成交升12.2%<br />\n<br />\n&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 雖然由「三馬」牽頭成立,標榜要「做有溫度的保險」的眾安保險(06060)要於本周四才掛牌,但機構投資者已率先在市場以暗盤方式買賣眾安股份。由於市場對眾安股份需求大,故暗盤一開已升逾60元,並在67元錄得成交,較其招股價59.7元,升12.2%。眾安今日暗盤價在67-69元之間叫價。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c15478e762361bcb76040d185259171fff8f3b","tid":413144,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T09:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無75蚊唔放"},{"pid":"fa264fec987bab2aa65711f1b47d0cec3dfea076","tid":413144,"uid":41849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:00:26.000Z","msg":"分派比率先係重點"},{"pid":"24607aeda24305c956a8ef49dcf7a4f2f101bb9d","tid":413144,"uid":8767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:03:59.000Z","msg":"抽得5手，有冇得中都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f7e1fda5c054ef6deb14fb6034afe9f37230a1","tid":413144,"uid":58249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:08:11.000Z","msg":"幾時知中唔中"},{"pid":"9cdc57ae121bdf497af37c7b7199fe6730a715a8","tid":413144,"uid":43016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:27:32.000Z","msg":"未撚見過派彩之前就有暗算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17deb3560a83448b11f81e7a3730a8214e187d3e","tid":413144,"uid":43016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09